query:
INSERT INTO dataset (
            dataset_id,
            paused,
            extra,
            modified_by,
            modified_date
        ) VALUES (
            $1,
            $2,
            $3,
            $4,
            $5
        ) ON CONFLICT (dataset_id) DO
        UPDATE SET
            paused = $2,
            extra = $3,
            modified_by = $4,
            modified_date = $5
        RETURNING
            dataset_id AS id,
            paused,
            extra,
            modified_by,
            modified_date
